Created the Checkers Game using a single array in Go language in Atom Text Editor
Pelase down the Atom Text editor from Google using https://atom.io/ link
Run the program in the command prompt in the specific path you have stored the Checkers file
Then run the game as go run checkers.go then press enter
It will ask the human to enter the numbers from which position it wants to move and then to which position it wants to move
indication the 8*8 table as below, the numbers starts from 1 till 64
